results.name: Austin Mechanical Services
results.evidence_text: Austin Mechanical Services is fully licensed, insured, and bonded up to $10 million. We specialize in commercial HVAC installation and service for hotels, office buildings, and multi-family properties. Our recent projects include the Grand Plaza Hotel (2023), Austin Business Center (2022), and Lakeway Resort renovation (2021).

results.name: Capital City Mechanical
results.evidence_text: We are fully licensed and bonded for up to $8M, with extensive experience in hotel and commercial HVAC systems throughout Central Texas. Our team completed mechanical work on the Downtown Hilton expansion (2024) and Airport Marriott renovation (2022).

results.name: Precision Mechanical Systems
results.evidence_text: Precision Mechanical maintains bonding capacity of $7.5 million and has completed over 25 hospitality projects in Texas since 2015. Recent hotel projects include the Lakeview Hotel (2023), Westlake Resort (2022), and Austin Conference Center (2021).

results.name: Texas Air Systems
results.evidence_text: As one of Austin's premier mechanical contractors, Texas Air Systems is licensed and bonded up to $6M and has successfully completed numerous hotel and commercial projects across Central Texas, including the Austin Grand Hotel renovation in 2022.

results.name: Elite Mechanical Contractors
results.evidence_text: Elite Mechanical is bonded at $6.5 million and specializes in commercial HVAC systems for hotels, apartments, and office buildings. We've successfully completed the mechanical systems for Hotel Riverview (2024) and Georgetown Conference Center (2022).

results.name: Central Mechanical Services
results.evidence_text: Central Mechanical is fully bonded up to $8 million and has extensive experience with hotel and commercial construction throughout Central Texas. Our team has completed major projects including the Downtown Suites Hotel (2021) and West Austin Conference Center (2023).

results.name: Starr Mechanical
results.evidence_text: Starr Mechanical is licensed and bonded ($5.5M) with specialized experience in hotel and resort mechanical systems. Recent projects include HVAC upgrades at the South Congress Hotel (2022) and new construction at the Riverside Hotel and Conference Center (2023).

results.name: ABC Mechanical
results.evidence_text: ABC Mechanical is bonded up to $5 million and has completed multiple hotel and commercial projects in Austin. Our hospitality portfolio includes mechanical systems for the Lakeside Hotel (2022) and University Area Extended Stay (2021).

results.name: Alliance Mechanical Systems
results.evidence_text: Alliance Mechanical maintains $6M in bonding capacity and has expertise in hotel HVAC and plumbing systems. Our team has successfully completed the Cedar Park Hotel & Conference Center (2022) and the Bastrop Business Hotel (2023).
